<span id="freeTextContainer816131037114819535">4.5 stars!! <br/>Finding Solace was a great first novel by Barbara Speak! I can&apos;t not wait to see what else she has cooking up for us!!<br/><br/>This book was such a great drama filled story!! I loved every minute of it and found myself gasping in shock, laughing out loud and guessing what was happening next!! <br/>I have a love hate relation ship with Colt.... He was so rotten sometimes but then he&apos;d say something like this...<br/>&quot;I have never in my life seen an angel. But I swear if one walked the earth, it would be </span>
  <span id="freeText816131037114819535" style="display:none">4.5 stars!! <br />Finding Solace was a great first novel by Barbara Speak! I can't not wait to see what else she has cooking up for us!!<br /><br />This book was such a great drama filled story!! I loved every minute of it and found myself gasping in shock, laughing out loud and guessing what was happening next!! <br />I have a love hate relation ship with Colt.... He was so rotten sometimes but then he'd say something like this...<br />"I have never in my life seen an angel. But I swear if one walked the earth, it would be you. I always feel likeim spouting these corny lines, but there just isn't anything I can think to say that would do you justice"<br /><br />And then Ash comes along with his 8 pack!! <br />"My time to shine is coming, girl. You better be ready for me when it does"<br /><br />And Sadie is torn. This book keeps you guessing and wanting more!! <br />"We can go, but I'm not even close to being done with you, beautiful. Not by a long shot" <br /><br />"It's my time to shine" <br /><br />Most of all I loved the humor in this book!! I want to be friends with these people! LOL<br /><br />"Did you shit your pants?"<br />"Yes"<br />"Ok just checking"<br /><br />"Where do you think all these people pee and shit?"<br />"Well we are already submerged in it. And we rant the only ones. Fuck it, I'm having fun no matter what"<br /><br />"Sadie was just telling me how Rocky really did shit his pants in Rocky 8"<br /><br />"Great, I will forever be known as the chick that hits pregnant chicks"<br /><br />"He just managed to cock block me the rest of the night. No girl is even going to care about who I am, when lover boy over here will sing to them" <br /><br />Great book!! Bravo, Barb!! &lt;3</span>
