<div id="review_794527286" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/794527286" />
    <a title="Kara Bailey" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16532021-kara-bailey"><img alt="Kara Bailey" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389293187p2/16532021.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/794527286?book_show_action=true">Dec 19, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kara Bailey" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kara Bailey" href="/user/show/16532021-kara-bailey">Kara Bailey</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer794527286" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2102539508306165379">5 breathtakingly beautiful stars. I want to give more!! This is already my favorite book of the year! I finished it 2 days ago and I am still emotionally recovering. This is THE book to beat this year! <br/><br/>First, let me start by saying that author Barbara Speak writes amazing characters. I connected with every single one of Sadie’s friends. Each time something happened with one my heart dropped or I squealed with joy! When the book ended, I was lost. I downloaded every song Sadie belted out and stil</span>
  <span id="freeText2102539508306165379" style="display:none">5 breathtakingly beautiful stars. I want to give more!! This is already my favorite book of the year! I finished it 2 days ago and I am still emotionally recovering. This is THE book to beat this year! <br /><br />First, let me start by saying that author Barbara Speak writes amazing characters. I connected with every single one of Sadie’s friends. Each time something happened with one my heart dropped or I squealed with joy! When the book ended, I was lost. I downloaded every song Sadie belted out and still feel every emotion I felt when reading that specific part.<br /><br />Sadie, oh Sadie. What a strong girl! She over comes so much in this book! Abusive relationships, tough decisions, and life shattering experiences. Throughout her story, Sadie has the most amazing group of friends that supports her 100 percent. Her friends helped make this story! You have every type of character here! Fighters, lovers, bad boys, good boys, and of course, the best friend! You also get drama at every corner!! THE LOVE TRIANGLE!! Man I am a sucker for those! Sadie is stuck choosing between Colt, the man that wont claim her as his and Ash, the man that quietly waits for his time to shine, and man does he shine! <br /><br />I could write about this story all night with a racing heart! Instead, go read it for yourself. I want to just shout it from the rooftop! READ THIS BOOK!! Thank you Barbara for setting the standards for 2014!<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2102539508306165379" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
