<span id="freeTextContainer1097466450258292745"> This book was amazing and made for a couple sleepless nights for me since that&apos;s my only real down time. I never wanted to put it down. This was the first time I had read anything by this author and she is awesome!!!! I never excepted what would happen next it was always a surprise and that was awesome because with some books you can predict the outcome before your even a fourth of the way done and with this book there was no way. This book is about Sadie Warren. She is a strong, loving, and ca</span>
  <span id="freeText1097466450258292745" style="display:none"> This book was amazing and made for a couple sleepless nights for me since that's my only real down time. I never wanted to put it down. This was the first time I had read anything by this author and she is awesome!!!! I never excepted what would happen next it was always a surprise and that was awesome because with some books you can predict the outcome before your even a fourth of the way done and with this book there was no way. This book is about Sadie Warren. She is a strong, loving, and caring woman that has gone through a lot in life but still hasn't been able to overcome it but you will learn how much she grows throughout this book. Colt is the handsome bad boy that just draws you like a magnet but never let's you get to close. Ash is literally alpha Prince Charming just waiting for his time to shine. Now you are probably wondering why I gave my description of these three and no they are not all in the same relationship all together. I described them because they all have big parts in this book at some point or another. And you will find out once you read it. This is seriously a must read!!!! I highly recommend it!!! Definitely a five star in my book!!! HAPPY READING!!!! </span>
