<span id="freeTextContainer4433369069034068305">****I was given this ARC for an honest review***<br/><br/>I don&apos;t say this often..In fact I can honestly say that this BOOK is only the 2nd book to ever touch me in away that I can easily relate too!!<br/>Best LINES EVER....&quot;You just have to remember what is meant to be, will be. It all works itself out in the end&quot;<br/><br/>Now on with the review...Buckle Up because its going to be a bumpy ride!!<br/><br/>This book is an EMOTIONAL ROLLER COASTER!!<br/><br/>You get to follow Sadie through her relationships..friends, lovers, boyfriends. We g</span>
  <span id="freeText4433369069034068305" style="display:none">****I was given this ARC for an honest review***<br /><br />I don't say this often..In fact I can honestly say that this BOOK is only the 2nd book to ever touch me in away that I can easily relate too!!<br />Best LINES EVER...."You just have to remember what is meant to be, will be. It all works itself out in the end"<br /><br />Now on with the review...Buckle Up because its going to be a bumpy ride!!<br /><br />This book is an EMOTIONAL ROLLER COASTER!!<br /><br />You get to follow Sadie through her relationships..friends, lovers, boyfriends. We get to experience it all. Sadie has been through SO much in her life and we get to see her GROW and LEARN...must have tissue!!<br /><br /><br /><br />Man this review is harder to write than I thought, I can't do it justice!! And, I REFUSE to do spoilers!! <br /><br />So with that said this is a MUST READ..I think EVERY WOMAN..hell even teenager can relate to Sadie on some level. <br /><br />Ok so I know I didn't give a lot away...SORRY, but you'll just have to trust me and read it for your selves this time!!<br /><br />So RUN..DON'T walk...go one-click it NOW!!!<br /></span>
